    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for those looking for value. The exterior shows its age with some visible paint fading on the roof and hood, along with a few minor scuffs and dings around the body. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows signs of regular use, including some wear on the upholstery and minor staining on the floor mats. Mechanically, the car is sound and starts reliably, though a buyer should anticipate upcoming maintenance such as new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid, functional vehicle that provides honest transportation.",
