    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m finally ready to part with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my weekend darling, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered with the best products. It looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom\u2014honestly, the finish is so deep you could dive right into it! It\u2019s been a dream to own and drives even better than it looks. I\u2019m looking for a good home for it, so if you\u2019re after a truly pristine ride that\u2019s been loved every mile of the way, come by and take a look. You won't be disappointed!",
