    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is an absolute specimen of German engineering, dialed in for the purist who demands surgical precision. We\u2019re talking about a chassis with zero cowl shake and a subframe that's been fully reinforced to handle the high-revving S54\u2019s torque curve with ease. The VANOS system has been completely overhauled with uprated seals, ensuring the variable valve timing remains razor-sharp across the entire power band. Compression numbers are consistent with factory tolerances across all six cylinders, and the cooling system has been refreshed to handle high-thermal loads without breaking a sweat. It sits on a staggered setup with fresh rubber, maximizing mechanical grip through every apex. The Getrag 6-speed shifts with the tactile feedback of a bolt-action rifle, and the limited-slip differential locks up predictably for perfect corner exit rotation. This isn't just a car; it's a meticulously curated driving machine with a pedigree that speaks for itself. No leaks, no codes, just pure, unadulterated performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
